		[JXTA&gt;<a href="http://www.jxta.org/">http://www.jxta.org/</a>]
is an open source project from Sun and is designed to make it easier
for developing P2P applications. JXTA provides basic features such as
peer discovery, peer groups, secure communications, portability on
different hardware (such as handhelds, laptops) etc. It provides basic
services on top of which many applications can be built. Key design
goal of JXTA is being modular. <br>
