	<tr><td bgcolor="#ffffff">
		&nbsp;The P2PXWiki provides following functionalities: (was posted in semantic of p2pxwiki task) 
<br>
<br>
&nbsp;1/ I got my wiki
<br>
&nbsp;2/ People can find my wiki while I'm there
<br>
&nbsp;3/ I replicate my wiki to the central server
<br>
&nbsp;4/ people can fall back and read my wiki on the central server
<br>
&nbsp;5/ I send my wiki to others
<br>
&nbsp;6/ People can read my wiki on other P2PXWiki users
<br>
